{
  "stem": "27507.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that was usually we went away for the whole two months for July/August.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we went as well to other places.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was a place called Orla, which was-- which is not very far from Warsaw, about maybe 50 kilometers or 60 kilometers.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that was a kind of a-- that was a village in a very beautiful place on the banks of a little river.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we went there, I think, once in '38 probably.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then I was very, very ill with diphtheria in 1939.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "After I recovered, we-- my parents rented a house there, and we went there to spend the summer.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But my parents traveled as well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They traveled elsewhere.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They went to France and to Italy and so on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But I didn't travel abroad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not yet.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not yet.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think we were meeting very often.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I remember only a few occasions.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember one occasion when my-- one of my mother's sisters, who was a doctor, who was a pediatrician, a child doctor, she married rather late in-- I think it was 1938.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember that's-- or maybe it was '37.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I might have been four then.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember that I was in the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember the lights and many people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And later on, there was a wedding reception in [POLISH], which was the street where my grandparents-- my maternal grandparents lived.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But unfortunately, I ate something but then I was not allowed to stay there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I think out of the excitement, I was-- I became sick, and I was not allowed to remain.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I was taken back home with-- being very unhappy about it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And those are basically-- there were other occasions.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
